i>\n<li><b>U\u017cywaj day parting z rozwag\u0105<\/b> &#8211; Nie traktuj day parting jako uniwersalnego rozwi\u0105zania na wysokie wydatki. Zastosuj t\u0119 strategi\u0119 tylko wtedy, gdy masz ju\u017c dobrze zoptymalizowan\u0105 kampani\u0119, aby zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 jej efektywno\u015b\u0107 w okre\u015blonych godzinach.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, kluczem do efektywnego zarz\u0105dzania bud\u017cetem reklamowym w kategorii suplement\u00f3w jest ci\u0105g\u0142a optymalizacja i analiza wynik\u00f3w. Pami\u0119taj, \u017ce day parting to narz\u0119dzie, kt\u00f3re powinno wspiera\u0107 ju\u017c udan\u0105 strategi\u0119, a nie by\u0107 jej g\u0142\u00f3wnym elementem.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h2>Jak skutecznie zarz\u0105dza\u0107 bud\u017cetem w reklamach suplement\u00f3w?<\/h2>\n<p>Czy zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, jak z<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":4778,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[4],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-4777","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-marketplace"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4777"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4777"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4777\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4778"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/